race.comment: CARAFE (2) went forward last time but couldn't quicken in the run home and finished seventh over 1400m at Orange. Among the top chances in what looks a most suitable race. EMBODIMENT (7) ended up 8 lengths behind the winner in ninth on debut over 1106m at Port Macquarie. Will take a lot from that experience. Likely to feature in this weaker race. FASHION SPREE (8) returns after four months in the paddock. Closed the last campaign with a fifth over 1350m at Beaumont (Newcastle). Nicely placed and can figure in the finish. TRIOLLI (11) missed the placings two runs back then settled well back last start when tenth over 1000m at Gundagai. Beautifully placed and is sure to play a pivotal role.
